update A new release of wxctl is available: 0.1.0 → 0.2.0
  Run `wxctl update` to upgrade
What's new in v0.2.0
  • wxctl update: upgrade in place from the CLI
  • What's new block in the post-command notice
  • Disable update checks with WXCTL_NO_UPDATE_CHECK
  run `wxctl update --notes` for all
